    <item>
      <title>北约盟国向乌克兰提供另外五套爱国者防空系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-allies-offer-ukraine-five-more-patriot-air-defense-systems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基在俄罗斯加强对乌克兰的袭击后请求北约提供更多帮助，美国总统乔·拜登表示，北约盟国将向乌克兰派遣五套远程防空系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-allies-offer-ukraine-five-more-patriot-air-defense-systems</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 22:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约在新的支持承诺中向乌克兰提供更多防空力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-set-to-boost-ukraine-s-air-defenses-and-send-f-16s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约盟国承诺向乌克兰提供五套远程防空系统，以表示对乌克兰的新一轮支持，尽管该国领导人拒绝向乌克兰提供加入北约的途径，且新的评估表明，北约与俄罗斯的冲突正走向无限期的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-set-to-boost-ukraine-s-air-defenses-and-send-f-16s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分裂的民主党人抨击特朗普议程以转移拜登的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管国会民主党人周二就是否支持乔·拜登参选展开争论，但白宫和立法者还是掌握了统一的策略：试图将话题从总统的敏锐思维转移到唐纳德·特朗普的政策目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:56:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普重返迈阿密竞选活动 拜登力挫反抗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/trump-taps-miami-for-return-to-trail-as-biden-fights-off-revolt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对手乔·拜登总统陷入激烈争论的同时，唐纳德·特朗普在数日的低调之后重新出现在竞选活动中，而拜登则顶住了党内要求其让位给更年轻的民主党候选人的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/trump-taps-miami-for-return-to-trail-as-biden-fights-off-revolt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
